Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读心术？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读人心声么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个经典能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新的能力者呀？ 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是个偏僻小巷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好…
