Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在这附近…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在原地等我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神速！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不可能是在等我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先去问问情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请教你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是身怀读心之类的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.88,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 真的吗 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 她点头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神速！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能请你对我用用读心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骂我大笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 没头没脑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都听见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 听见友利同学说高城同学是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城是个肌肉笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！连着损我是什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又听见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再确认一下 你们都过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是肌肉笨蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是ZHIEND笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张口闭口全是ZHIEND…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看来这孩子听取心声时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是自己听到 还能让旁人也听到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 ZHIEND笨蛋是啥意思?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢骂ZHIEND?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你先骂我的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在心里想想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁允许你偷听心声了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还是想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我在 大家就会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本无处可去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先离她远点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 你们听不见我的心声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半径约为两米半么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这个范围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被会她的能力暴露心声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来就像当事人在说话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种能力…没法控制吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少她是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则也不会有刚才那种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是因为暴露了朋友和家人的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄出过不少乱子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只能一个人躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说过这种持续发动的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样 应该是有诱因的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把诱因找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能力就让她一直发动着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和柚咲琳一起努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和黑羽同学一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些恶心的妄想会酿成大祸的 知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽同学也别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一个人去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才不是说 大家都会吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人怎么吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说反了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在她身边却不吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能让她的疑虑减轻些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等等 你觉得我们听着彼此的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能不吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得能行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我俩可是大冤家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这是个增进友谊的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能推心置腹地交流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然要依赖能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕失败就随你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为她好 我们一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你俩可以走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.36,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 柚咲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.45,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.08,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心声 我不用能力也能听到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也在翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不一起去玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上这位大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们不会再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才吵过 说不吵她也不信么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想的都是正经事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有本事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想去的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在这里很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能就地解散就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 踹人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这叫吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他耍愣 我这搭档就得马上吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们是搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一唱一和 关系很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 这叫吐槽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责吐槽的这么说 当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要负责耍愣 说的话就不能全信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没骗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我饿了 想吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 那就去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 附近有个家庭餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊绪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫你小伊喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊选好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要意式白汁乌冬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是开口说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式白汁乌冬…这玩意好吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我就点杯热咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要印度烤鸡和印度奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙要冰淇淋苏打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读心术真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我乱点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多久没吃饭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一顿是前天的晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就再没回过家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 不管这些 玩个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去哪玩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园 动物园 水族馆之类？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那就游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 工作日里 人就是少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先坐哪个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中？飓风？听名字就不是好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂有宇既怕高又怕快么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝无此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是直白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你照样得陪我们坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一起来玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙说他快挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是再坐一次吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再坐一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要坐吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是直白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去死亡之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之塔…有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 不会真死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3…2…1…0
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥胆子真小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 好想揍她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你耍愣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点冰淇淋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气如我 居然落魄至此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然觉得自己很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表挺帅 但是很胆小 不够看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够看？居然敢说小爷我不够看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说为啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你耍愣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没耍愣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么衰的我 可不能让同学们看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看到了哦 这可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是求人的态度么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拜托了」在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别说出去 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你苦苦相求 就答应你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 我不会说出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的没吵架呢 明明在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过啦 我们是关系很好的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系很好 是在交往吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定是在谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？明明很般配…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？她是认真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你耍愣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没耍愣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我们接着玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丫头搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的约会都给她毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么说小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你是个成熟的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友道了歉 你倒耍起小孩脾气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我招你惹你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就憋了一肚子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别憋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的关照 后会无期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 一番心血尽付东流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能追啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 尽付东流是啥意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近我就会变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请让我们走近你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！肯定会变得不幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我不能从命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我消失好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会让你落单的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有特殊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让可怜的女孩不再孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请让我留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我再相信一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 又在一起喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们…陪在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉永远都不会分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是来自我强烈的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个从小一起玩的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 她突然开始和另一群人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再陪我玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我去问她 她也不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我默默许愿 想听听她的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这就是诱因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望一直没变对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她离开你的理由后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该就能控制自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很想听她的心声 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没等我听到心声 大家就开始吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能跑开 甚至离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情 你弄明白了也无能为力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我们来帮你解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不会骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了小伊 我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你今天就在我家过夜吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭也好红
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披萨酱 看我怎么收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在那女孩身边时才会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我好像告诉过她号码…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是友利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小伊的好朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是穗乃花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小伊的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找到她了 她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么担心小伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还要避开她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再和她扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是想请教一下理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你是她朋友 那我更不能说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们不是小伊的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要说的 都是重要机密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请勿外传
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她失踪前 你们学校有过一场骚乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把肚子里的话全说出来 吵成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的特殊能力引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能让周围人的心声暴露在外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量 出现在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…你在逗我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们隶属于一个收集·统领能力者的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他都身怀特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 我是个透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 他会把你的手机交到我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我上？好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 这是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有…这种能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 小伊也变成了一名特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拉她入伙 我们在暗中抓住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我说这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要带她离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会让她在我们道上干活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们永远都不会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我来问问你这个好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在离别之时 有没有话想对她说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点人情味 我还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们道上干活…这不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后她会…动不了的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？说给我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶然听妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊她…得了不治之症…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…她能跑能玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才决定离开她！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意保持距离！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其看着最要好的朋友衰弱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如在那之前讨厌她！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要讨厌她！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我最喜欢的小伊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我最讨厌的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样 算哪门子的好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你和别人玩耍时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病魔正侵蚀着她的身体啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好意思说什么「最要好的朋友」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了一个人逃避 就不会干点别的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想后悔一辈子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说句话啊！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开穗乃花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃花 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此激动的友利 我从来没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 她是在为一起玩过的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为她身上无来由的不幸而愤怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读心术的能力者 后来怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利不让我说 我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…但是我很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是萝莉控？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能？我心中只有柚咲琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好 晨会开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道读心术的能力者 后来怎样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和友利 会在放学后定期探望她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃花也下定了决心 一直陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利那次激愤的谴责 没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊绪里也接受了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定和病魔作斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…女性的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 女性可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有一天 你也会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会为了某个人 努力向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别不相信 人生就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻 谈什么人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻 为了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要努力向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 友利姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.28,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:29.68,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香你看 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很强大啊
